This folder contains an example using the etcd package with ssl. To run this we need a etcd cluster with ssl enabled.


To test it in a docker environment:
The docker-compose file will build the containers, run an etcd cluster of 3 containers with ssl enabled and run the sample code in etcd_ssl.go.

Navigate one level up: cd ../../

run it:
docker-compose -f etc-ssl-docker-compose.yml up

To stop it:
docker-compose -f etc-ssl-docker-compose.yml stop

To remove it:
docker-compose -f etc-ssl-docker-compose.yml rm -f
